Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全机保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种速度和操控的确有威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的行动方式有一定的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的攻击会从正面过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要正面冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的攻击被回避掉后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了防止接下来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他会立刻移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,读取移动资料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,S57
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种场合的下一个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是往后方移动保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐标是X23
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看破了我们算计他的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请给下一步的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止的全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在布里塔尼亚有母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有学友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是突然而来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本军在将人型自在战斗装甲骑KnightMare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,投入实战的布里塔尼亚军面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无法抵抗而被击破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又要被交给别的人家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是枢木的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要去本家那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这种奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是在垃圾场的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会把布里塔尼亚毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自称是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站在护灵车的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那时发誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决不原谅夺走我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉的双眼和双腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朱雀人生的布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把世界毁坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有都改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可要公布了啊  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我死了这件事就会被公开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽全力让我们逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的男人也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个男人交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚卿  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给他们  谁也不许出手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚卿  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽全力放过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬畏我们  追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的名字是  黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在有力量的人攻击没有力量的人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会再出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论那敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有多么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有力量之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畏惧我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无力之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界  由我们黑色骑士团来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要某个人胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我成为了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,建立了黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才睡着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样你也不用敲我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修佛德学园学生会副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我表面的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为布里塔尼亚学生过着无聊的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的问题就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个喜欢庆典的学生会长喜欢给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男女逆转庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对静音宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猫祭典  还要化装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里还能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她说了我还是会奉陪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有那个『小学生的一天』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事都默许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从来到这个学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉变的总是充满笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  现在朱雀也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从7年前那个夏天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分别至今的朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让他们知道我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样平日的生活就会被毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不保护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只猫怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那个假面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把刚才看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 该用时还是要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是学生会长米蕾·阿修佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:08:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立即去抓在校内逃窜的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,课外活动全部暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,协助我们的社团可以享受经费优待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来追猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  学生会长说要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猫就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我比较擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上次小鸟逃掉的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把那么久的事拿出来提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一如既往的体力笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前明明更加个人主义的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事都在我计划的范围以内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那台白色的KnightMare出现以前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向导兵器Z01 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用SandBoot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用最大战速沿液状斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援总督
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  想要问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你极端讨厌人的死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但却愿意在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让人死才会在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种纯真总有一天会害死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是吗  又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲二式把白壳的家伙毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的突破力是个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挡下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全军  向撤退路线移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再下去会成为消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是能源没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特派报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  朱雀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想自从那时开始那家伙就改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,称呼自己为『我』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明以前是自称『本人』的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\rSTAFF}[前者『僕』相对比较谦卑  后者『俺』相对比较自我主义]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在学校还是装作不认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去做警察  从内部改变不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的做法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只会坐收渔人之利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来改写事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以审判者自居来得到胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话什么也改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由错误的过程得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到的朱雀是更加个人主义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着自己和日本的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,率直的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此而令他泪流满面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个意义上来讲并不是全部都改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  确实有所不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要救人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想获救的是你自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以自己想要找死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以总是让自己前往死地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的善意只不过是自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想要得到惩罚的撒娇男孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你改变的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟有那么大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直自己背负着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是被死板的规则所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是成为布里塔尼亚的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到我的身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚已经是一个不值得你去效忠的国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想要把它改变成有价值的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从布里塔尼亚的内部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为用错误的方法得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是没有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个小时  军事法庭就要开庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个法庭是为了让你成为犯人而策划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,检察官也好  法官也好  辩护律师也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那样  这也是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会开始打压11区住民和名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前  我朋友也总是这么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的缺点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也想抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这儿反而会被反制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都是要死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为了大家而死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个笨拙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从以前开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就是因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为就是这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才觉得是配得上娜娜莉的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可能一直陪在娜娜莉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不是日本人 你为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道能够实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不得不完成这事的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果按现在的计划一切顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要踏上去吗  修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果  这是我的命运的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉能够敞开心房面对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是11 应该是叫枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是克洛维斯殿下那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么11在KnightMare里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终止影像  这后面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不惜歪曲道理也要活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就按照预定把我处刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能在那种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该在娜娜莉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是为了这个而来到这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然落魄到成为满足现状的没出息的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使否定现在的社会也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被人承认而得到能够改变这一切的力量才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就按那条路走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是输是赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不使出全力是不会有任何收获的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于国家还是个人都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  要抓住他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木准尉Harken Boost解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,密码是我的最爱食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别继续战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的已经达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用3号道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来回答刚才的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是否决定了哪位来当我的骑士的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定的成为我的骑士的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那里的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀要成为由菲米娅的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让搜查工作能够确实进行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人助了我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,17岁的话就应该去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时有这个权限的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以朱雀才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要救的人是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的话一切都合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择了由菲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们  而是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有另一招可用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把胜利握在手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道了那个白壳的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是朱雀这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家长期的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次将把
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二期的OP　解読不能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及ED　モザイクカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有OST CD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,节目特制电话卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从C.C.那儿夺来的CHEESE君Q版魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起送给10人作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够参与的只有使用MVS的手机登陆手机网页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁修·Vi·布里塔尼亚下令全力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是我的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够保护娜娜莉的男人成为了由菲米娅的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是为了保护黑色骑士团的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我来决定吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能不顾全大局吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让世界成为我所希望的样子
